title: Ancient Temple of Fire
story: The temple is situated deep in the dense jungle, in uncharted lands. Lately it was squatted by a gang of pirates.

notes.text: A great stone door with a keyhole to the west.
A weird, sticky to touch cube hovering in the middle of the large room.
A gnome. Pleads to borrow rations.
A petrified body of an elf, a key close to it.
Some gold and a rusty javelin in a box.
